    <item id="import-auto-id1677107">An isolated system is defined to be one for which the net external force is zero <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mfenced open="(" close=")"><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mtext mathvariant="bold">F</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>net</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mfenced><m:mtext>.</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math></item>
